Wildrider swiftly dodges to the left of the shells, and continues
upwards, a sick and twisted smirk on his face. He raises his gun and
fires once more.

Speedbreaker moans and groans. "ohhhhhhhhh, my head" he tries to
transform, but can't. He figueres the crash he made into the rock in
robot mode must have damaged his robot mode transformation. He wished he
had hit it in car mode. He slowly backs up, and ungracefully crawls
(drives slowly) towards the big crater he saw Beastbox fall into.
